+        # incompatible boxmot (e.g. a major bump that moved the tracker classes,
+        # making the top-level ``boxmot.BotSort`` lookup raise AttributeError)
+        # lands here. Degrade to the built-in tracker instead of hard-crashing,
+        # mirroring the "boxmot not installed" path — tracking never hard-fails.
         if want_reid:
-            # ReID weights/download failed — fall back to motion-only so tracking
-            # still works (never let an optional appearance model kill tracking).
+            # ReID weights/download may simply have failed — retry motion-only
